The following tables include summarized financial information of the obligor groups of debt issued by T-Mobile USA, Inc., Sprint
and Sprint Capital Corporation. The summarized financial information of each obligor group is presented on a combined basis with
balances and transactions within the obligor group eliminated. Investments in and the equity in earnings of non-guarantor
subsidiaries, which would otherwise be consolidated in accordance with GAAP, are excluded from the below summarized financial
information pursuant to SEC Regulation S-X Rule 13-01.
