administrative on our Consolidated Statements of Comprehensive Income.
Our Merger restructuring initiatives also include the acceleration or termination of certain of our operating and financing leases for
cell sites, switch sites, retail stores, network equipment and office facilities. Incremental expenses associated with accelerating
amortization of the right-of-use assets on lease contracts were $1.7 billion, $873 million and $153 million for the years ended
December 31, 2022, 2021 and 2020, respectively, and are included in Costs of services and Selling, general and administrative on
our Consolidated Statements of Comprehensive Income.
